{"url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/issues/47224", "repository_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust", "labels_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/issues/47224/labels{/name}", "comments_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/issues/47224/comments", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/issues/47224/events", "html_url": "https://github.com/rust-lang/rust/issues/47224", "id": 286444435, "node_id": "MDU6SXNzdWUyODY0NDQ0MzU=", "number": 47224, "title": "Regression with NLL and RefCell", "user": {"login": "abusch", "id": 506344, "node_id": "MDQ6VXNlcjUwNjM0NA==", "avatar_url": "https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/506344?v=4", "gravatar_id": "", "url": "https://api.github.com/users/abusch", "html_url": "https://github.com/abusch", "followers_url": "https://api.github.com/users/abusch/followers", "following_url": "https://api.github.com/users/abusch/following{/other_user}", "gists_url": "https://api.github.com/users/abusch/gists{/gist_id}", "starred_url": "https://api.github.com/users/abusch/starred{/owner}{/repo}", "subscriptions_url": "https://api.github.com/users/abusch/subscriptions", "organizations_url": "https://api.github.com/users/abusch/orgs", "repos_url": "https://api.github.com/users/abusch/repos", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/abusch/events{/privacy}", "received_events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/abusch/received_events", "type": "User", "site_admin": false}, "labels": [{"id": 604489711, "node_id": "MDU6TGFiZWw2MDQ0ODk3MTE=", "url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/labels/A-NLL", "name": "A-NLL", "color": "f7e101", "default": false, "description": "Area: Non Lexical Lifetimes (NLL)"}, {"id": 650731663, "node_id": "MDU6TGFiZWw2NTA3MzE2NjM=", "url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/labels/C-bug", "name": "C-bug", "color": "f5f1fd", "default": false, "description": "Category: This is a bug."}], "state": "closed", "locked": false, "assignee": null, "assignees": [], "milestone": null, "comments": 11, "created_at": "2018-01-06T00:50:52Z", "updated_at": "2018-06-29T19:22:16Z", "closed_at": "2018-06-29T19:22:16Z", "author_association": "NONE", "active_lock_reason": null, "body": "Hi,\r\n\r\nI have some code similar to the one below that compiled fine up until nightly-2018-01-03, but stopped compiling starting with nightly-2018-01-04:\r\n\r\n```rust\r\n#![feature(nll)]\r\nuse std::cell::RefCell;\r\n\r\nstruct Foo {\r\n    pub v: Vec<u32>,\r\n    pub b: u32,\r\n}\r\n\r\nfn f(foo: RefCell<Foo>) {\r\n    let mut foo = foo.borrow_mut();\r\n    \r\n    foo.v.push(foo.b);\r\n    \r\n}\r\n\r\nfn main() {\r\n    let foo: RefCell<Foo> = RefCell::new(Foo {v: Vec::new(), b: 0});\r\n    f(foo);\r\n}\r\n```\r\n\r\nThe error I now get is\r\n```\r\nCompiling playground v0.0.1 (file:///playground)\r\nerror[E0502]: cannot borrow `foo` as immutable because it is also borrowed as mutable\r\n  --> src/main.rs:12:16\r\n   |\r\n12 |     foo.v.push(foo.b);\r\n   |     ---        ^^^ immutable borrow occurs here\r\n   |     |\r\n   |     mutable borrow occurs here\r\n\r\nerror: aborting due to previous error\r\n\r\nerror: Could not compile `playground`.\r\n\r\nTo learn more, run the command again with --verbose.\r\n```\r\n\r\nI was able to work around it by coercing `RefMut<T>` to a `&mut T` using `let foo = &mut *foo.borrow_mut()`, and normal nll rules work as expected. But since it used to work with `RefMut`, I suppose it still should?", "closed_by": {"login": "nikomatsakis", "id": 155238, "node_id": "MDQ6VXNlcjE1NTIzOA==", "avatar_url": "https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/155238?v=4", "gravatar_id": "", "url": "https://api.github.com/users/nikomatsakis", "html_url": "https://github.com/nikomatsakis", "followers_url": "https://api.github.com/users/nikomatsakis/followers", "following_url": "https://api.github.com/users/nikomatsakis/following{/other_user}", "gists_url": "https://api.github.com/users/nikomatsakis/gists{/gist_